            <p><strong>What it is:</strong> Translation by a UAE Ministry of Justice licensed translator. Bears official MOJ stamp, signature, and license number.</p>
            <p><strong>Starting price:</strong> AED 150+ per document</p>
            <p><strong>Required by:</strong> Dubai Courts, GDRFA, MOFA, MOHRE, MOHESR, Abu Dhabi Courts</p>
            <p><strong>Verify:</strong> MOJ Hotline 800 333333, License #701</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-card certified">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3>Certified (No MOJ)</h3>
            <span class="card-badge">Private / Banks / HR</span>
          </div>
