            <p><strong>What it is:</strong> Translation by a professional translator with a signed accuracy declaration. No MOJ stamp.</p>
            <p><strong>Starting price:</strong> AED 100-150 per document</p>
            <p><strong>Accepted by:</strong> Banks, private companies, HR departments, some free zone authorities</p>
            <p><strong>Limitation:</strong> Not accepted by courts or most government entities</p>
          </div>
        </div>

