          <div class="card-header">
            <h3>Notarized</h3>
            <span class="card-badge">Embassies / Specific Legal</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p><strong>What it is:</strong> Certified translation verified by a Notary Public. Notary confirms translator's identity, not translation quality.</p>
            <p><strong>Starting price:</strong> AED 200+ per document (translation + notary fee)</p>
            <p><strong>Required by:</strong> Some foreign embassies, specific cross-border legal contexts</p>
            <p><strong>Note:</strong> Most UAE domestic submissions do not require notarization</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

