            <p><strong>No</strong> (stays within DIFC/ADGM/company): Continue to question 3.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="decision-step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Does the receiving entity specifically request MOJ?</h3>
            <p><strong>Yes:</strong> Get MOJ-certified translation.</p>
            <p><strong>No or unsure:</strong> Certified translation is sufficient. You can always upgrade to MOJ later if needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

